\mt1 2 TIMOTI
\mt2 Khe Por Phenat…®t…®gap Timoti Ndi Khergi Gap
\imt1 Khe fharav gan…®nga buni khare.
\ip Timoti Por phorgap, mani mba Ňčaara bavira mbui guma ma. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, Por ana muunga t…®vir vhuuin ana kh…®vav, kha gava khergiap, Timoti ndi mbai, ana mba t…®vi z…®n Ňčg…®rga. Timoti, ana Zisas khoth…®gi nd…®knd…®k kuemkueg…®rga fhuvara. Ana vh…®ra Zisas Kraisa buna vhuueŇč bun nzuai t…®va thamtharga fhu. Ana guigi guarara, Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč, ana nta z…®n Ňčg…®rga. Mba gumgi zaagi gum simt…®gir ana nd…®…®i, ana khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip, Fhe Bak…®me ana n…®…®Ňčgi Ňčaar, ana anan muunga.
\ip Timoti vh…®ra, ana khuarar mba fhura tamtam buni nzuav, pham buni nzuai nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč ki fhuv gumgi, ana khuarar mbe bunin r…®g…® thari. Mba buni mbararagi gumgi, mba khesharigi buni mben k…®r…® t…®vir farfagi. Timoti, Por mbui t…®vi, ana nta nd…®knd…®g…®p, nta z…®n Ňčg…®ri. Mba t…®vi khare, guigira khaŇč t…®gap havhargiap, Zisas khoth…®gi t…®v, ndava m…®…®t…®ga ndigap ki t…®v, guigira harigi nt…®…®ri vuzvugap, mbark…®rga simt…®gi ndi. Timoti mba t…®vi z…®n Ňčg…®ri.
\c 1
\ms1 Timoti khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip, Ňčgar…®p, Fhe Bak…®me, Ňčaara guma guar k…®ri.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Ef 1.1\x*Gu Por, Krais Zisas farasarigi Ňčaara guma ma. Fhe Bak…®me, ana wo vuzvugara na farasarigim, gu anan Ňčaara guma kav, gu guigira Zisas Krais khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, ana mben n…®…®n zav suaŇčgi k…®r…® t…®vi, gu nta bun mbe nzuai.
\p 
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt FG 16.1; 1 T 1.2\x*Timoti, ndu nan kam fara muuŇčgim, gu guigira wo ndavar ndu n…®…®Ňčgi. Gu kha gava khergiap, ndu ndi mbai. Nza Ndia Fhe Bak…®me gum nza Bak…®me Zisas Krais, mani guigira wani won ndavanin ndun n…®…®Ňčv, ndun korar muuŇčv, ndava m…®…®t…®gar ndun n…®…®Ňčrim, ndu k…®ri.
\s1 Nza Fhe Bak…®men buna vhuuen mber…®rga fhu.
\p 
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt FG 22.3; 23.1; Ro 1.8-9; Fi 3.5; 1 Te 1.2; 3.10\x*Nan nz…®gi, mbe wari wo ndavi vheri kaŇčgiap, mbe guigira Fhe Bak…®me n…®man Ňčgarav, mbe t…®var vhuuŇčra z…®n vov, Fhe Bak…®men Ňčaara muuŇčgi. Gu ntigem mba khesharigi t…®vara z…®n vov Fhe Bak…®men Ňčaara mbui. Gu vh…®ra won ndav vhee kaŇčgi. Gu big…®n mbat…®k thueŇč muuŇčgip ne nzuav ana n…®man simt…®k ki fhuvara. Gu raa gu maan ana phorga nzuav, gu ndu nd…®knd…®gap Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav anan ndikndigi.
\v 4 Gu ndu thee ri ne nd…®knd…®gap, gu guigira taagip ndu gangirganeŇč vuzvugi. Gu ndu gangip, gu guigira ndikndig…®rga.
\v 5-6 \x - \xo 1:5-6 \xt FG 16.1; 1 T 1.5; 4.6\x*\x - \xo 1:5-6 \xt 1 Te 5.19; 1 T 4.14\x*Gu guigira khueŇč kaŇčgi, ndun nz…®k Rois gum ndu niamuuŇč Unis, mani fhum guigira Krais khoth…®gi t…®vara muuŇčgiap, ndu Krais khoth…®gi. Ndu khaŇč t…®gap havhargiap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi t…®v, gu ana nd…®knd…®gap, gu ndu nd…®knd…®ga khavi. Ndu mba Fhe Bak…®me won Ňčaara muun zav fhura ndu n…®…®Ňčgi big…®n, ana khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip ndun k…®ri. Mba big…®n, ana khaŇč muuŇčgip ndun k…®ri, guma vhav shiav kim, ana wom ana beregi, ana fogap k…®vgi fara muuŇčgi. Gu mba farver ndu kh…®ngim, Fhe Bak…®me fhura ndu n…®…®Ňčgi ŇčkasŇčka, gu ana nzuai.
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Ru 24.49; FG 1.8; Ro 8.15\x*Ndu kaŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®me won Ňäinan nza n…®…®Ňčgi, ana r…®r…®var nza nd…®…®i Ňäina fhuvara. Ana ŇčkasŇčkar nza nd…®…®i Ňäina ma. Ana nza mbuim, nza guigira wari won ndavir harigi nt…®…®ri ga nd…®…®v, ana vh…®ra nzan kurkurigim, nza tuituigia piigiap, ana nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇčra z…®n Ňčg…®p, t…®vir vhuuiŇčra muunga.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Ro 1.16; Fi 1.7; Kor 1.24; 1 T 2.6\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, ndu nza wo Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč bun suangen mber…® thari. Ndu vh…®ra nan mber…® thari, gu ana khuav b…®nan ki guma ma. Ndu Fhe Bak…®me han ŇčkasŇčka ndigip, na phorg…®p Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč bun nzuai nen simt…®ga ndiri.
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Ro 8.28; Ef 1.4; 2.8-9; 1 Te 4.7; Ta 3.5; Hi 3.1; 1 Pi 1.20\x*Fhe Bak…®me taagia nza ndigap, nzan kamgim, nza anan gumgi gu mbigi k…®rga. Ana nza mbui t…®vir vhuuiaŇč nd…®r…®gap, nzan kamgi fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Ana fhum guarara, Fhe Bak…®me zumgum kha nuian gu bigi ga muuŇčgi, ana fhum guarara ana wo vuzvug…®ra, ana nza kora muuŇčgiap, nzan kamgi. Ana Krais Zisasan farve panan, ana nza kora muuŇčgim, nza anan gumgi gu mbigi ki.
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt 1 Ko 15.54-57; Kor 1.26; Hi 2.14; 1 Pi 1.20\x*Ntigem, kha tugen Krais Zisas, ana taagia nza ndi guma ma. Anan kora muumbar ntigem k…®rar h…®gi. Krais Zisas rimgiap, za vh…®zi ŇčkasŇčka, ana ana vh…®zgiap, ana won buna vhuuen panan, ana mba gumgi gu mbigi ga muuŇčgim, mbe zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč, mbe ana kaŇčgi.
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt 1 T 2.7\x*Ana mba buna vhuueŇč bun suangen na vuzvugi. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgiap nan farasarigim, gu Fhe Bak…®men buna vhuueŇč bun nzuav, gu ana farasarigi Ňčaara guma kav, gu Fhe Bak…®me vuzvugi t…®vir gumgi gu mbigi kh…®vav, mbe nzuai.
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt Ef 3.1-2; 1 T 6.20; 2 T 4.8; 1 Pi 4.19\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, gu mba simt…®gi ndi. Gu nen mberi fhu. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Gu mba khoth…®gi guma, gu ana kaŇčgi. Gu vh…®ra khueŇč kaŇčgi, ana nan farve kh…®ngi buna vhuueŇč, ana tuituigip ne gan…®nga, mba buna vhuueŇč nzerara k…®v Ňčg…®p, Krais taagia zirga tuga bak…®men h…®g…®rga.
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt 1 T 1.10; 4.6; 6.3; 2 T 2.2; 3.14; Ta 1.9; 2.1; Hi 10.23\x*Gu khar ndu nzuai buni guari, ndu tuituigip nta nd…®knd…®k suirari. Ndu nta suirav, ndu gu gumgi gu mbigi kh…®vav, mbe nzuai t…®va z…®n Ňčg…®p, mbe suaŇčri. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, ndu khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip, nza guigira Krais Zisas khoth…®gap, guigira wari won ndavir harigi gumgi ga nd…®…®i, gumgi gu mbigi mbui t…®vara suira havhargip, nza guigira Kraisan gumgi gu mbigi k…®v, nza khaŇč t…®g…®p mba t…®va phuni suirav havhargiri.
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt Ro 8.11; 1 T 6.20\x*Fhe Bak…®me ndu farve kh…®ngi buna vhuueŇč, ndu tuituigip ne gan…®ri, ne guigira big…®na vhuuŇč guareŇčra, ndu tuituigip ne gan…®ri. Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar nzan vhen ki, ana ndun kurkurarim, ndu tuituigira mba buna vhuueŇč gan…®ri.
\p 
\v 15 Ndu kaŇčgi, Esia Ňčgu bak…®me fhain ki gumgi, mbe za na thagim, Figerus gum Hermogenes, mani vh…®ra na thagi.
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt 2 T 4.16; 4.19; Zu 1.21\x*Gu Guma Bak…®me phorga nzuai, ana Onesiforus gum, ana muuŇč gu tari, ana phenan ki nt…®…®ri, ana mbe korar muunga. Tugi vh…®rver Onesiforus na mbuim, nan ndava vhee nzerara ki. Ana gu phena t…®vanen ki, nen nan mbergi fhu. Zak…®ra fhuvara!
\v 17 Ana Roman z…®gap, ana khaŇč t…®gap na nzuav gari. Ana na nzuav garav kav, ana zumgum na gangi.
\v 18 Gu ana korar muun zav, ana nzuav Guma Bak…®me phorga nzuai. Ana Fhe Bak…®me za kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi ga suaŇčv mbe suanga tuga bak…®men, ana anan korar muunga. Ndu tuituigiap khueŇč kaŇčgi, Onesiforus, ana Efesus Ňčgu bak…®men, ana vh…®ra Ňčaari vh…®rver nan kurigi.
\c 2
\s1 Timoti Krais Zisasan ntari ga mbui guman vhuuŇč k…®ri.
\p 
\v 1 Ndu nan kam Timoti, nza Zisas suaŇčgi t…®vi z…®n vov, ndu maaŇč muuŇčgiap Fhe Bak…®me guigira wo ndavar nza nd…®…®i t…®var panan havhargiri.
\v 2 Ndu za na mbararagim, gu gumgi vh…®rve n…®man mba suaŇčgi buni, ndu mba bunin Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč suira havhargi gumgi ga suaŇčrim, mbe vh…®ra mba bunin harigi gumgi kh…®v…®v, mbe suaŇčri.
\p 
\v 3 \x - \xo 2:3 \xt 1 T 1.18; 2 T 1.8; 4.5\x*Ndu Zisas Kraisan ntara guman vhuuŇč k…®ri, ndu nza harigi gumgi mba Ňčaarar simt…®ga ndi, ndu nza phorg…®p, mba Ňčaarar simt…®ga ndiri.
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt 1 Ko 9.25\x*Ndu ntari gumgi mbui t…®v, ndu ana kaŇčgi. Mbe ntari ga mbui gumgi kav, mbe shoga ruav, mbe harigi Ňčaari phorga mbui fhu. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Mbe ntari gumgi kav, mbe nzerara ntari ga mbua rui, mbe maaŇč muunga, mbe gari guman pan mbe vuzvug…®rga.
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt 1 Ko 9.25-26; 2 T 4.8\x*Guma harigi guma the kambara saŇčv khuafurga, ana mba harigi guma khuash…®rarga t…®vi, ana nta z…®n vui. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgirga fhu, ana mba guma khuafuav harigi guma khuash…®rav ndi big…®n, ana ana ndigirga fhu.
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt 1 Ko 9.7; 9.10\x*Guma ana Ňčaara mbat…®ga mbuav m…®na bak…®men pargiap, ana gangana vhuun ana muuŇčgi, mba guma, ana fharav mba m…®nan mba ndigirga.
\v 7 Ndu gu kha suaŇčgi buneŇč, ndu ne nd…®knd…®g…®rim, Guma Bak…®me, ndu nd…®knd…®gar muuŇčrim, ndu mba buneŇč kaŇčgip, ndu mba buni n…®…®Ňčge kaŇčgirga.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 2:8 \xt Ro 1.3; 2.16; 1 Ko 15.1; 15.4; 15.20\x*Ndu zazera Zisas Krais ga nd…®knd…®g…®ri, ana rimgiap taagia khavgi. Ana Ňčgui vh…®rve gari guman pana Devitan nz…®ga mbe ma. Gu nzuai buna vhuueŇč, ne bun nzuai.
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt FG 9.16; 28.31; Ef 3.1; 3.13; Fi 1.7; 1.12-14; Kor 4.3; 4.18\x*Gu mba buna vhuueŇč bun nzuai, mba buna n…®…®eŇčra, kha gumgi na garim, gu guma mbat…®k ma. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap mbark…®rga simt…®gir na nd…®…®v, na ndiv phena t…®vaneŇč kh…®ngi. Mbe maaŇč na mbuim, Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč ne b…®nan keg…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara.
\v 10 \x - \xo 2:10 \xt 2 Ko 1.6; Ef 3.13; Kor 1.24\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, gu won ndava havhargiap, gu zam mba simt…®gi ndi. Gu mba Fhe Bak…®me won mbuigi gumgi gu mbigi, gu mben kurkurarga. Gu vuzvugi, mbe vh…®ra Krais Zisas taagiap mbe ndigirim, mbe ana han zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč ndigip, mbe guigira nzerara ana phorg…®p zazera mbara muuŇčgip k…®rga.
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt Ro 6.5; 6.8; 2 Ko 4.10-11; 1 T 1.15\x*Kha kameŇč ne guigi guarara,
\b
\q1 ‚ÄúNza maaŇč muuŇčgip guigira ana phorg…®p rimgirga, nza vh…®ra ana phorg…®p zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč ndigip, ana phorg…®p k…®rga.
\q1 
\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt Mt 10.33; Ru 12.9; Ro 8.17; 1 Pi 4.13\x*Nza maaŇč muuŇčgip th…®g…® havhargip, nzan hi simt…®gi, nza za nta ndirga, nza vh…®ra ana phorg…®p, Ňčgui vh…®rve gari gumgir pani k…®rga.
\q1 Nza k…®r ana seg…®p, ana z…® ndiv zaaheg…®rga, ana vh…®ra k…®r nza seg…®p, nza ndi zaaheg…®rga.
\q1 
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt Nam 23.19; Ro 3.3-4; Ta 1.2\x*Nza maaŇč muuŇčgip, ana z…®n Ňčg…®r saŇčv suaŇčgip, nza mba kameŇč z…®n Ňčg…®p, ana z…®n Ňčg…®rga fhu, ana wo suaŇčgi kameŇč, ana nera z…®n Ňčg…®rga.
\q1 Ana wo suaŇčgi kameŇč, ana nduara ne dorg…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara.
\q1 Zak…®ra fhuvara!‚ÄĚ
\s1 Timoti khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip Ňčgar…®v, guigira Fhe Bak…®men Ňčaara guma guar k…®ri.
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt 1 T 1.4; 5.21; 6.4; Ta 3.9\x*Ndu zazera mba gumgi gu mbigir kurkurarim, mbe kha kameŇč nd…®knd…®g…®ri. Ndu Fhe Bak…®me n…®man, ndu kama havharar mbe suaŇčri, mbe mba bigi kh…®ni gum bigi bisarire ga suaŇčv wari kaadog…®p, wari daaŇč thari. Mba khesharigi buni, nta guma then kurarga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Mba buni mbararagi gumgi, nta guigira mben mpirmpir…®ga t…®vir farfagi.
\p 
\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15 \xt 1 T 4.6; Ta 2.7-8\x*Ndu khaŇč t…®g…® havhargip, Ňčgar…®v, guigira Ňčaara guma k…®rga, Fhe Bak…®me ndun Ňčaara vuzvugirga. Ndu maaŇč muuŇčgip, guigira Fhe Bak…®me buna guareŇč, ndu tuituigira ne n…®…®Ňč sh…®g…®rga, ndu ana n…®man mber…®rga fhu.
\v 16 \x - \xo 2:16 \xt 1 T 4.7; 6.20; Ta 1.14\x*Ndu fhura mba tamtam nzuai buni, mba Fhe Bak…®me nd…®knd…®gi z…®n vui fhuv buni, ndu k…®r nta seg…®ri. Nta Fhe Bak…®me nd…®knd…®gi z…®n vui fhuvara. Mba khesharigi buni, nta pim gumgi ndiav k…®r Fhe Bak…®me si tuavar vui.
\v 17 \x - \xo 2:17 \xt 1 T 1.20\x*Mba khesharigi buni, nta vh…®ra guman farfagi suman fara muuŇčgi, ana shiv Ňčg…®v, guigira k…®vgirga. Mba khesharigi buni nzuai gumani khare, Himeneus gum Firetus.
\v 18 Mani buna guaren tuav, mani ana thagi. Mani khaŇč muuŇčgi ne nzuav, mani kha buni nzuai. Nza guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, Fhe Bak…®me taagia nza khavgi. Mani maaŇč nzuaim, mba guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi mbari, mbe Zisas khoth…®gi nd…®knd…®k, mani anan farfagi.
\p 
\v 19 \x - \xo 2:19 \xt Nam 16.5; 16.26; Ais 52.11; Nah 1.7; Zo 10.14; 10.27; Ro 8.35; 1 Ko 8.3; 1 Zo 2.19\x*Mani maaŇč mbuim, Fhe Bak…®me ana won siosan muun zav, won k…®na havharage ndi kh…®ngi niŇčge th…®gi. Mba k…®niŇčge th…®ga havhargiap ki. Ana mba k…®niŇčgen, ana kha kameŇč khergi, ‚ÄúGuma Bak…®me, ana won gumgi gu mbigi, ana mbe kaŇčgi.‚ÄĚ Ana vh…®ra kha kameŇč khergi, ‚ÄúMba za Guma Bak…®me z…® ndigi gumgi, mbe k…®r t…®vi mbat…®gi ga segi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 20 \x - \xo 2:20 \xt Ro 9.21; 1 Ko 3.12; 1 T 3.15\x*Phena bak…® mben, mbe gor gu sirvar muuŇčgi thuuri gu bigi ki. Mbari, mbe khirar muuŇčgi, mbari mbe nuianan muuŇčgi. Mba thuuri mbari, mbe ntan Ňčaari vhuuiaŇč mbui, mbari mbe harigi Ňčaarir, nta mbui.
\v 21 \x - \xo 2:21 \xt 2 T 3.17; Ta 3.1\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, guma ana won ndava vura t…®vi mbat…®gi thav, ana Fhe Bak…®me n…®man Ňčgarigi. Mba guma, ana mba thuuŇč mbe fara muuŇčgi, mbe anan Ňčaara vhuuŇč guarara muunga. Ana guigira Fhe Bak…®men guma guarara k…®v, ana wo Guma Bak…®men kurkurarga. Ana anan kurav za mbar k…®rga Ňčaarir vhuuin muunga. \fig Mbe mbark…®rga bigir pheni ga muuŇčgi. (2.20)|src="HK00144C.tif" size="col" copy="Horace Knowles/Louise Bass" ref="2.20"\fig*
\p 
\v 22 \x - \xo 2:22 \xt FG 9.14; 1 Ko 1.2; 1 T 1.5; 6.11\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, ndu mbark…®rga vuzvugi mbat…®gi, nta gumgir Ňčkaa ndavi khavi, ndu k…®r mba vuzvugi ga seg…®ri. Ndu k…®r nta seg…®p, ndu Fhe Bak…®me t…®va guara suaŇčv Ňčgar…®v, guigira Zisas khoth…®gi t…®v, guigira won ndavar harigi nt…®…®ri ga nd…®…®i t…®v, ndava m…®…®t…®ga ndi t…®vi, ndu mba t…®vi ndiri. Nde zam mba t…®vir muuŇčri. Ndu phorgap nde Fhe Bak…®me n…®man guigira Ňčgarav ki gumgi, mbe guigira Zisas khoth…®gap taagip wari ndir zav anan kaai gumgi gu mbigi ma.
\v 23 \x - \xo 2:23 \xt 1 T 4.7; 2 T 2.16; Ta 3.9\x*Ndu mba nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč ki fhuv gumgi, mbe fhura pham tamtam buni nzuai, ndu k…®r mbe seg…®ri. Ndu kaŇčgi, mba khesharigi buni, nta wari daav, ntari khavi buni ma.
\v 24 \x - \xo 2:24 \xt 1 T 3.2-3; Ta 1.7-9; 3.2\x*Guma Bak…®men Ňčaara guma, ana ntarir muuŇčv, vheg…® thari. Ana t…®vir vhuuin za mba gumgir muuŇčri. MaaŇč muuŇčgip, gumgi ana r…®…®Ňčr…®…®Ňčrim, ana wo ndav shir…® mbevav, Fhe Bak…®me vuzvugi t…®vir mba gumgi gu mbigi kh…®v…®v, mbe suanga tuavir vhuuiŇč ndi gan…®ri.
\v 25 \x - \xo 2:25 \xt Ga 6.1; 1 T 2.4; 6.11; Ta 1.1; 1 Pi 3.15\x*Ana mbarara mba buni daasui gumgi, ana mbe nd…®knd…®gi ndiv th…®gar maaŇčv, mbe suanga. Ana maaŇč muunga, Fhe Bak…®me maaŇč muuŇčgip, mben kurarga, mbe ndavi domdorgip tuituigip buna vhuueŇč kaŇčgirga.
\v 26 Satan won vhia mbe ndigap, wo buni mbararav, wo z…®n Ňčg…®r zav, mbe mbui. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgip, buna guareŇč kaŇčgirga, mbe nd…®knd…®gi taagip tuituigip bigi kaŇčgip, mbe Satanan vhia thav k…®rar heg…®p, b…®kb…®…®girga.
\c 3
\s1 Zisas taagi zir…®rga tuk han mbararga, gumgi t…®vi mbat…®gir muunga.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt 1 T 4.1; 2 T 4.3; 2 Pi 3.3; 1 Zo 2.18\x*Ndu khaŇč muuŇčgip kaŇčgiri, Zisas taagi kha nuianan zir…®rga tugar, simt…®gi mbat…®gi guarira, nta k…®vgip, kha nuianan h…®rga.
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt Ro 1.29-31; 1 T 1.20; 6.4; 2 Pi 2.3; 2.12\x*Gumgi warira vuzvug…®p, mbe guigira Ňčk…®…®a suaŇčv thaginen muunga. Mbe wari wo z…®ri ndiv vun kuamkuav, fhura ndikndig…®p, fhura vheg…®p buni mbat…®gir harigi gumgi ga suanga. Mbe wari wo ndegi gu ndegmbori nzuai buni, mbe nta daaŇč suv, t…®vir vhuuin mbe mbui gumgi, mbe mben ndikndig…®rga fhu. Mbe k…®r Fhe Bak…®men t…®vi ga seg…®rga.
\v 3 \x - \xo 3:3 \xt Ta 2.3; 2 Pi 3.3\x*Mbe harigi gumgir k…®vntogi k…®rgane kaŇčgi fhu, mbe big…®n the suaŇčv vheg…®rga, mbe mba ntara vh…®zgirga tuav ki fhu. Mbe fhura sh…®sh…®g…®p, bunin harigi gumgi ga s…®v, mbe suanga. Mbe wo mbui t…®vi, mbe tuituigip nta gan…®nga fhu. Mbe fhura tamtam gumgi ga vheg…®p mben farfarga. Mbe t…®vir vhuuiŇč, mbe panan nta keg…®rga.
\v 4 \x - \xo 3:4 \xt Fi 3.19; 2 Pi 2.13; Zu 1.4; 1.19\x*Mbe t…®vi mbat…®gir wari won k…®vntogira muunga, mbe wari won nd…®knd…®gi mbat…®gira z…®n Ňčg…®rga. Mbe kha nd…®knd…®gar muunga, mbe nduarira gumgir ruu ma. Mbe guigira kha nuianan mbark…®rga t…®vi, mbe ntan ndikndigirga, mbe nta vuzvug…®p, mbe Fhe Bak…®me vuzvugirga fhu.
\v 5 \x - \xo 3:5 \xt Mt 7.15; 7.21; Ro 2.19-20; 2 Te 3.6; 1 T 5.8; 6.5; Ta 1.16\x*Mbe fhura, wari wo fhavi ga sh…®sh…®g…®p, Fhe Bak…®men t…®vi z…®n Ňčg…®rga. Mbe guigira Fhe Bak…®men ŇčkasŇčka mbevav, mbe ana nd…®r…®g…®rga fhu. Ndu mba khesharigi gumgi, ndu mbe thav, samra k…®ri.
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt Mt 23.14; Ta 1.11\x*Mba khesharigi gumgi, mbe nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč ki fhuv mbigir phenin Ňčg…®rga tuavi ndi gari. Mbe vov, mben raaŇč shav, mbe nd…®knd…®gi garim, mbe mbe vuzvugi z…®n vui. Mba mbigi, mbe t…®vi mbat…®gi vh…®rve ga muuŇčgiap, mbe mba t…®vir simt…®ga ndiav ki. Mbe kim, mben vuzvugi mbat…®gi mbe khavav, mbe Ňčgim, mbe mbark…®rga t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui.
\v 7 Mba mbigi, mbe guigira harigi guma mbe kh…®v…®v, mbe suanga buni mbararageŇč vuzvugi. Mbe Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč, mbe ne kaŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara.
\v 8 \x - \xo 3:8 \xt Kis 7.11; Ro 1.28; 2 Ko 13.5; 1 T 6.5; 2 T 2.25\x*Fhum Zanes gum, Zambres, mani panan Moses ga kegi. Mba t…®vara, t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui gumgi, mbe panan buna vhuueŇč ga kegi. Mbe nd…®knd…®gi za Ňčangim, mbe guigira Zisas khoth…®gi t…®v za mbat…®gi. \f a \fr 3:8 \ft Mbe ZudaiŇč kha neŇčg…®a mbui. Zanes gu Zambres, mani mba Ňčgui vh…®rve gari guman panan bigi heei gumani ma. Mani mba Moses regi tuger mani Idz…®van Ňčgui vh…®rve gari guman panan bigi heei gumani ma. Ndu Taagia Ndi o, Kisim Bek 7.22 gan…®v, vh…®ra 9.11 gan…®ri. \f*
\v 9 Mbe mbui t…®vi k…®vgirga fhu. Mba gumgi mben t…®vi gan…®nga, mbe guigira ŇčanŇčangi. Mba gumgi fhum Zanes gum Zambres garim, mani ŇčanŇčangi fara muuŇčgi.
\s1 Timoti khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip Fhe Bak…®men buna vhuueŇč suirari.
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 3:10 \xt Fi 2.22; 1 T 4.6\x*Ndu, Timoti, ndu fhum na phorga kegap, gu Fhe Bak…®me vuzvugi t…®vir gumgi kh…®vav mbe nzuai t…®v, ndu ana kaŇčgi. Ndu ana kaŇčgiap, ndu vh…®ra gu rui t…®vi, ndu vh…®ra nta kaŇčgiap, ndu nan t…®vi, ndu guigira za ntan n…®…®Ňčge kaŇčgi. Ndu vh…®ra khueŇč kaŇčgi, gu guigira khaŇč t…®gap havhargiap Zisas khoth…®gap, zazera mbarara won ndava havharav, gu Ňčgarav, guigira won ndavar guigira nza phorgap Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi ga n…®…®Ňčgiap, havhargia kav, nan hi simt…®gi, gu nta ndi.
\v 11 \x - \xo 3:11 \xt Sng 34.19; FG 13.14-52; 14.1-20; 2 Ko 1.10\x*Mbe na muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi, gu ntan zaagi ndi ndu kaŇčgi. Mba gumgi Antiok, gu Aikoniam, Ristran na muuŇčgi t…®vi ndu vh…®ra nta kaŇčgi. Ndu mbe kha Ňčgui bak…®vir na muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi guarira, ndu nta kaŇčgi. Mbe maaŇč na mbuim, Guma Bak…®me nan kurigim, gu mba simt…®gir vhen, gu nzerara kegi.
\v 12 \x - \xo 3:12 \xt Mt 16.24; Zo 15.20; 17.14; FG 14.22; 1 Te 3.3\x*KhueŇč guigi guarara, za Krais Zisas phorgap Fhe Bak…®men t…®vi z…®n vui gumgi, kha gumgi t…®vi mbat…®gir mben muunga.
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt 2 Te 2.11; 1 T 4.1; 2 T 2.16\x*Mba gumgi mbat…®gi gum fhura Fhe Bak…®men z…®n vui nen wari ga sh…®sh…®gi gumgi, mbe kha gumgi gu mbigi guiguigirga. Satan vh…®ra mbe guiguigirga, mben t…®vi guigira za mbat…®girga.
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt 1 T 1.13; 2.2\x*Mbe maaŇč muunga, ndu mba ndigi kameŇč, ndu khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip ne khoth…®g…®p, ndu khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip ne suirari. Nza mba kamen ndu kh…®vav ndu suaŇčgi gumgi, ndu nza kaŇčgi.
\v 15 \x - \xo 3:15 \xt Zo 5.39; 1 Pi 1.20-21\x*Ndu kaŇčgi, ndu taranera kav, ndu Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gavi, ndu nta kaŇčgi. Mba gavi nta nd…®knd…®gi vhuuin ndun n…®…®nga, ndu Krais Zisas khoth…®g…®rga, Fhe Bak…®me taagi ndu ndigirga.
\v 16 \x - \xo 3:16 \xt Ro 15.4; 2 T 2.21; 2 Pi 1.20-21\x*Fhe Bak…®me bunin vhuuiŇč, nta za Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaarar ŇčkasŇčka ntan ki. Mba buni, nta guigira bunin vhuuiŇč ma. Nta buni guarir nza kh…®vav, mba nd…®knd…®gi mbat…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, nta mbe nd…®knd…®gi ndiv th…®gar mbav, vh…®ra nzan k…®r…® t…®v gu bigi ndiv th…®gar mbav, vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me t…®va guarar nza kh…®vav, nza nzuai.
\v 17 \x - \xo 3:17 \xt 1 T 6.11; 2 T 2.21\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, mba buni nza Fhe Bak…®men gumgi gu mbigi, mba buni nza muuŇčgim, nza guigira za mba t…®vi guari ndirga. Nza nta ndig…®p, nza za mba Ňčaari vhuuin muungane tukt…®g…®r za mbui.
\c 4
\s1 Timoti khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip, Fhe Bak…®men buna vhuueŇč bun suaŇčri.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 4:1 \xt FG 10.42; Ro 14.9-10; 1 T 5.21; 6.13\x*Gu Fhe Bak…®me gum Krais Zisas, ana zumgum za kha vh…®zgi gumgi gu mbigi, gum kha Ňčamki gumgi gu mbigi muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi ga suaŇčv mbe suanga guma, gu mani n…®man kama havharar khaŇč ndu nzuai. Krais Zisas, ana za kha gumgi gu mbigi n…®man k…®rar h…®g…®p, ana zazera mbara muuŇčgip k…®v, Ňčgui vh…®rve gari guman pan k…®rga.
\v 2 \x - \xo 4:2 \xt FG 20.20; 20.31; 1 T 4.13; 5.20; Ta 1.13; 2.15\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, ndu khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip, anan buna vhuueŇč bun suaŇčri. MaaŇč muuŇčgip, gumgi ana buna vhuueŇč mbarararga o, mbe ne mbarara thagi, ndu zazera khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip Krais buna vhuueŇč bun suaŇčri. Ndu kama havharar mbe suaŇčv, mbe ndavi gor…®v, mbe ndavi khav…®rim, mbe ndavi domdor…®v, mben nd…®knd…®gi ndi th…®gar maaŇčrim, mbe Fhe Bak…®men t…®vi z…®n Ňčg…®rga. Ndu zazera mbarara mbe suaŇčv, Fhe Bak…®me vuzvugi t…®vir mbe kh…®v…®v, mbe suaŇčri.
\v 3 \x - \xo 4:3 \xt 1 T 1.10; 4.1; 2 T 1.13; 3.1; 3.6\x*Ndu mbarara. Zumgum, gumgi buni vhuuiŇč mbarara tharga. Mbe thav, mben khuari harigi khesharigi buni mbarara saŇčv z…®gz…®g…®rga. Mbe gumgi vh…®rvera ndirga, mbe mbe mbararargeŇč vuzvugi buni, mbe ntan mbe kh…®v…®v mbe suanga.
\v 4 \x - \xo 4:4 \xt 1 T 1.4; 4.7; Ta 1.14\x*MaaŇč muunga, mbe k…®r buni guari ga seg…®p, mbe wari wo khuarir mba nz…®gi gu nzari kh…®nin t…®g…®rga.
\v 5 \x - \xo 4:5 \xt FG 21.8; Ef 4.11; 2 T 1.8; 2.3\x*Mbe maaŇč muunga, ndun nd…®knd…®k zazera kaŇčgira k…®ri. Ndu mba simt…®gi gu zaagi ndirga. Ndu Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč bun gumgi gu mbigi ga suaŇčri. Ndu kha gumgi gu mbigir kurkurarga Ňčaar ki. Ndu Fhe Bak…®me Ňčaara guma ma, ndu guigira za mba Ňčaarar muuŇčri.
\s1 Por r…®m…®nga tuk han mbai.
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 4:6 \xt Fi 1.23; 2.17; 2 Pi 1.14\x*Ndu kaŇčgi, gu r…®m…®nga tuk han mbarigi. Gu rimgirga, na v…®z…®n, mbe mba Fhe Bak…®me nzuav ofa mbui wain farar muuŇčgip si suarga. Gu Ňčg…®rga tuk han mbarigi.
\v 7 \x - \xo 4:7 \xt 1 Ko 9.24-25; Fi 3.14; 1 T 6.12; Hi 12.1\x*Gu won k…®r…® t…®va nzuav khuaf…® vhuuŇčra muuŇčgi. Gu ntigem zav mba khuaf…® vh…®z…®rga thaan h…®gap, gu guigira Fhe Bak…®me khoth…®gi t…®v, gu ana suirav havhargi.
\v 8 \x - \xo 4:8 \xt 1 Ko 9.24-25; 2 T 1.12; Ze 1.12; 1 Pi 5.4; VB 2.10\x*Ntigem, guma big…®na ndir zav, ana nzuav khuafuv, mba khuaf…® kambarav, mba big…®na ndi. Mba big…®n, Fhe Bak…®me ana bevahegim, ana nan rarga mbur ki. Mba big…®n, ana khaŇč muuŇčgi. Guma Bak…®me, t…®vir vhuuiaŇč mbui guman nan kam…®nga. Guma Bak…®me, ana t…®var vhuuŇčra z…®n vuav, kha gumgi gu mbigi muuŇčgi t…®vi ga nzuav mbe nzuai. Ana mba gumgi gu mbigi muuŇčgi t…®vi ga suaŇčv mbe suanga tuga bak…®men, gu mba khuaf…® kambarigi ne suaŇčv ana mba big…®nan nan n…®…®nga. Ana mba big…®nan nara n…®…®nga fhu. Fhuvara. Ana mba big…®nan za ana gan…®rim, ana k…®rar h…®r za mbuim, guigira ne vuzvugiap ana rarga ki gumgi, ana za anan mben n…®…®nga.
\s1 Timoti vhemkora Por han z…®ri.
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 4:9 \xt 2 T 1.4\x*Timoti, ndu khaŇč t…®g…® havhargip, tuav the gangip, vhemkora nan han z…®g…®ri.
\v 10 \x - \xo 4:10 \xt 2 Ko 8.23; Ga 2.3; Kor 4.14; Fm 1.24; Ta 1.4; 1 Zo 2.15\x*Ndu mbarara! Demas na thagi. Ana kha nuianan t…®vi, ana guigira nta vuzvugiap, ana Tesaronaika Ňčgu bak…®men vugi. Kresens, ana Garesia Ňčgu bak…®me fhain vugim, Taitus ana Darmesia Ňčgu bak…®me fhain vugi.
\v 11 \x - \xo 4:11 \xt FG 12.12; 12.25; 13.13; 15.37-39; Kor 4.10; 4.14; Fm 1.24\x*Ruk nduara nan han khar ki. Ndu maaŇč muuŇčgip, Makar kuv, Ňčko z…®ri. Ana nan kurav Ňčgar…®rga guman vhuuŇč ma.
\v 12 \x - \xo 4:12 \xt FG 20.4; Ef 6.21-22; Kor 4.7-8\x*Gu Tikikus ga sarigim, ana Efesusan vugi.
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 4:13 \xt FG 20.6\x*Ndu z…®r saŇčv, gu ruga hav shari fhava shaara mpeeŇčge gu niŇčge ndi Troas Ňčgu bak…®men Karpus phena t…®gi, ndu niŇčge ndigi z…®ri. Ndu niŇčge ndiv, ndu vh…®ra mba gavi phorg…®v ndigiri. Ndu vh…®ra tuituigip gan…®ri, ndu muuŇčv k…®v, mba dama nderar muuŇčgi gavi, ndu nta nd…®knd…®k Ňčangirga.
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 4:14 \xt Sng 28.4; 62.12; Snd 24.12; FG 19.33; Ro 2.6; 1 T 1.20; VB 18.6\x*Areksander, ana brasan bigi kari guma ma. Ana t…®va mbat…®gar na muuŇčgi. Ana zumgum ana mba muuŇčgi ne suaŇčv, Guma Bak…®me muumbara mbat…®gar anan muuŇčgirga.
\v 15 Ndu vh…®ra mba guman r…®v…®ri. Ana guigira panan nza kha nzuai buna vhuueŇč, ana guigira panan ne ga kegi.
\p 
\v 16 \x - \xo 4:16 \xt FG 7.60; 2 T 1.15\x*Gu fhara guarara mbe na nzuav nzuaim, gu th…®gap nzuaim, guma the na khoth…®gap, gu nzuai kameŇč ana nan kurav, ne suaŇčgi fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Mba gumgi za na thagi. Gu Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai, ana mbe muuŇčgi big…®na mbat…®geŇč, ana ne nd…®knd…®g…®rga fhu.
\v 17 \x - \xo 4:17 \xt Sng 22.21; Dan 6.22; FG 23.11; 27.23; 2 Pi 2.9\x*Guma Bak…®me, ana nduara nan mpia kegap, ana ŇčkasŇčkar na n…®…®Ňčgim, maaŇč muuŇčgiap, gu za mba harigi fhaiŇč Ňčgui gumgi, gu Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuuen mbe nzuaim, mbe ne mbararagi. Fhe Bak…®me nduara raion th…®…®ni t…®n na ndigi.
\v 18 \x - \xo 4:18 \xt Sng 121.7; Ro 11.36; Ga 1.5; Hi 13.21\x*Mba t…®vara, mbe nan muunga t…®vi mbat…®gi, Guma Bak…®me na t…®n nta ndigirga, gu nzerara k…®rim, ana na ndigip wo gari Ňčgu Hevenan ndarga. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap nza zazera ana z…® ndiv vun kuamkuarga. Ne guigi guarara.
\p 
\v 19 \x - \xo 4:19 \xt FG 18.2; 2 T 1.16-17\x*Ndu nan raar vhuuŇč ndiv Prisira gum Akuiran n…®…®Ňčv, vh…®ra nan raar vhuuŇč ndiv Onesiforus gu muuŇč gu tari, ana phenan ki nt…®…®ri, ndu anan mben n…®…®Ňčgiri.
\v 20 \x - \xo 4:20 \xt FG 19.22; 20.4; 21.29; Ro 16.23\x*Erastus, ana Korin Ňčgu bak…®mera ki. Trofimus, ana r…®…®im, gu ana thav ana ndim, Miretus Ňčgu bak…®mera t…®gap z…®gi.
\v 21 Ndu khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip tuav gangip, vhemkora nan han z…®g…®ri. Ndu maaŇč muuŇčgip k…®v k…®rim, ruga hi tuk h…®g…®rga, b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč bak…®vi khav…®rga.
\p Uburus gum, Pudens, Rinus, Krodia gum, khaŇč guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe wari won raar vhuun ndu nd…®…®i.
\p 
\v 22 Guma Bak…®me ndu phorg…®p k…®ri. Ana korar muumbar za nde phorg…® k…®ri.
